# Transform Logic

Transform Maps control how data moves from Import Set tables to target tables.

Source Table:
u_employee_import

Target Table:
u_employee_directory

Field Mapping:

employee_id → u_employee_id
name → u_name
email → u_email
department → u_department
title → u_title
manager → u_manager
status → u_status

Transform scripts also normalize data values and validate fields.
